Features
Fully parameterized: table, partition column, batch size, parallelism, cleanup.
Shadow + stage table approach → zero downtime.
Parallel partition loading reduces migration time.
Batch insert + partition SWITCH → fast and minimal log usage.
Delta catch-up ensures no lost data.
Dynamic recreation of all nonclustered indexes.
Validation logging for each partition in MigrationLog.
Optional cleanup of old table.
Production-ready for hundreds of millions to billions of rows.
This is now a fully auditable and reusable production migration template for Azure SQL.